    "title": "Bank of Baroda is Hiring: Credit Analyst (Senior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Bank of Baroda! We are hiring a Credit Analyst for our Raipur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Bank of Baroda:\nBank of Baroda is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bank of Baroda!",
